Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Kenta Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's hard to admit, but l've never had any luck with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since Suwatee and her friends moved in, my life's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got to *BEEP* Kaori AND Misao, one right after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems like there's an endless supply of girls to *BEEP* *BEEP*!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee is sweet, and Shuree is a nosy loudmouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l'm turning into some kind of animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a natural, beautiful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a new girl stepped into my love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who landed right in front of me is Chisato Sugita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, l feel destiny again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Can Bunny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Can Bunny\NExtra 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. l haven't been sleeping much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This comic is almost exactly like ''X-2''.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you write it, Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you watch X-2, Kenta? l'm a huge fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space Detective X-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An otaku girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you shown this to a publisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l'd be embarrassed to show it to someone l didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt just so happens that l'm working part time at Shudansha, the comic publisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, l'll introduce you to the editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! l'm so lucky l met you, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How fortunate, Kenta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl who thinks she can count on you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Go, Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five more girls...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kenta, l wish you would realize how l feel about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... this can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Northern Emperor Shibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, do you know why l am here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's because l stole the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must return the seven stars before the full moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else become my one thousandth wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, lf you use the star to touch a human man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will lose all memory of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's been awhile since l enjoyed a virgin like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Then l'll pick up the manuscript tonight. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The art and plot are fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, you're a big Space Detective X-2 fan, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of people are following that trend in comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you want to be a star, you need your own style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for our New Manga Competition is soon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you could enter a finished copy of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, it's such a surprise to see Kenta bring a girl here all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it is one of your best qualities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not going to enter the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With exams next year, if l stop going to class, my mom will kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if l cut back on how much l sleep, it'll be like it was earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, since having Aya see it, l'm feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully quiet. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell your cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, okay? lt's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, come on in, Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not a great room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What, is this girl with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, please use this\Nroom as often as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta, are you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, a girl, you old wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? How many times have you done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm the lead actor. Come and see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? Only kids are interested in that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-2! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, this poster is a present for Kenta's new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Kenta! Have fun doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Earth is turning round in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth is like a blue pearl in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spaceman said this beautiful Earth is for you and for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty lame disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This imagery allows us to see the Earth as...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, she's been hard at work for three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was all my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just wanted to give Chisato time to write her comic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please don't tell her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. lt's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so sweet of you to want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l feel a little jealous of Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l see a happy couple, l can't help wanting to tempt the man a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's pretty tempting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe how much he gets laid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting so weird. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so good, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there... deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think l'm going to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Squirt it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much! There's so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the comics you wrote got thrown away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom found them while l was at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had most of the new one in my bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the deadline is so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't have time to both study and re-draw the missing parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me so much, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm really sorry. l feel-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, l'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked so hard. lf we work together, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, l've finished drawing that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then fill in the colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's determined to finish the comic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to exhaust himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm the first one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days it's hard to find a man like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so good, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kenta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, how's Kenta doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, l... l...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Chisato take care of him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Kenta. lt's my fault you're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine in no time. He's just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just needs to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.44,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiryuka Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kenta, l promise you l won't give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l finally finished it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the comic for the contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fantastic, Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you stay here with me all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working on the manga, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best medicine l could get.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, forget about Kenta,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let's go home. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the promise Suwatee made to the Northern Emperor Shibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright you guys, what did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and tell Kenta it's over and return the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the star l can make love to Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, l wouldn't remember any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought if Kenta would treat me like a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would be able to leave everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l don't want to forget about Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love him, but we can't be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want to become Emperor Shibi's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! l just want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let go of me! l want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, l wish Kenta would realize how much you love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.58,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Space Detective X-2 Show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't wait to hear about the contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you win, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l gave it my best shot. Even if l lose, l'm happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to X-2?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't it starting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-2! X-2! Aren't you here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-2! X-2! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki, you idiot! You hurt your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably did it screwing some girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Saiki's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Chisato, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big X-2 fan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki, you bastard. You set us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's hoping Kenta doesn't screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling okay, Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't slept much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine! l feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l get to be X-2! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-2! X-2! X-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up you brats! X-2 has abandoned you all! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space Detective X-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Spirit! l warned you not to hurt children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't lecture me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, evil doers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This costume is so hot, and it's heavy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l feel faint.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... l must get up! l must get up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What's wrong? Stand up, X-2! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of the air! Gather to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide that which can be seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show that which is hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend thy strength... to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, Space Detective X-2 is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you cheer, he'll get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shuree, why are you going so far?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all sing the X-2 song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.42,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}With his hands...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all sing the X-2 song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.96,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}...he banishes evil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.43,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}For the sake of the ones we love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:35.90,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}The sign of the galaxy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't let the kids down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're cheering for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:42.36,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}...Space Detective, X-2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waruda, you're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Star Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, X-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteorite Drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lron Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, that's good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Special COMET BAZOOKA KlCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, that was terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray! X-2 won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l did it, Kenta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks for bailing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop by the office later, and l'll pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Kenta. l got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll remember this day, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll go change now-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's really hot inside this costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel a little better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me. l'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sweaty. lt's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt don't mind... if it's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it alright, Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt feels so intense...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, l'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:05.69,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiryuka Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they charge so much for two nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, you're paying for your fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel a source of strong spiritual energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out in the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a huge flower garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. lt's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe how big it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that beautiful woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People with strong spiritual sense can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, she's no one special!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now l remember. You were my nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm really just a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Haruna. Haruna Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a beautiful garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my grandfather said there used to be a church here before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of his looks after the garden now that he's passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relatives? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.20,0:24:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Uncle Okamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going? Did you find your lost necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l'm still looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to go have another test now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, l need to keep looking for my necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.12,0:24:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.85,0:24:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that l think of it, you really are quite beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.82,0:24:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! What are you saying all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you don't say that to every girl you meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.88,0:25:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought l'd dropped it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.99,0:25:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.59,0:25:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.60,0:25:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
